<hw>Trend</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Clean wool.</def> <mark>[Prov.
Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trender</ent>⟦br⟧
